habitat_description:
This species occurs from the coastal area of southern Texas, inland Texas, and well into coastal Veracruz, Mexico (Axtell 1983).  Occurrences of this species have been reported abundant inland and in coastal zones. However, it has been described to prefer coastal dunes where the burrows of small mammals or crabs provide shelter(Bartlett and Bartlett 1999).

Commonly found on coastal dunes, barrier islands, and sandy areas (Axtell 1983, Bartlett and Bartlett 1999).
